creator: Dev Nain
descriptionHtml:
Hey, Text Writer, are you looking for the best or top-rated English dictionary or translation app?
If yes then come and join us with the English-to-Urdu translation app. English Urdu Translation
Dictionary is a learning application, designed to facilitate Urdu-speaking users. So, no matter
whether you are searching from English to Urdu or from Urdu to English you can easily find the
meanings of your respective words in this app. who are keen to learn English to Urdu
translation and pronunciation. You can convert your written data into English or Urdu through
the English Urdu dictionary. This translator is free and you are able to translate words or
sentences quickly, conveniently and easily. This offline English-Urdu dictionary translation will
help you translate your data offline or without the internet. English Urdu Dictionary is
presented to you with amazing or eye-catching graphics which compel you to use it. English
Urdu dictionary has auto-suggestion with offline dictionary mode. This is especially beneficial
for worldwide users who want to find Urdu to English and English to Urdu meanings of difficult
words in this dictionary. Mobile based English to Urdu and Urdu to English Dictionary is ideal
for everyone especially for everyone like students, employees and for all. And best helpful
for English Learner.

Features:
- Download for free English to Urdu Dictionary.
- Amazing User Interface.
- Easy to use.
- Offline English to Urdu dictionary app.
- Auto suggestion without internet.
- Proper Grammar help.

This is the best Urdu English dictionary for travelers, business mans, Students, teachers,
learners, boys and girls, English to Urdu dictionary will help you find English words
translations antonyms, synonyms with history and study plans or shareable data with others.
